author: Che Guevara
text:
Sometimes you don't let your mouth speak, rather your conscience.

Between you and God. You've no dirt on him, those you've supported over the years are so evil that you know in a sane society they should be hung.

Nigeria is a country where people defend their thieves. https://t.co/NzIm9BKRTd

author: Che Guevara
text:
Aren't you aware of these happening over the years?

There you come with high service, which will only lead to more agony for the masses. If they made the mistake of voting candidates like you.

We want candidates who stood by people all the times. Not your type, sir. https://t.co/kA29EEA2ep

author: Che Guevara
text:
You deserve so much more in life, you've proved to be a genuine activist whose only concern is for the well-being of the masses.

Your message is loud and clear enough for anyone sane Nigerian.

You have risked so much for liberation like fela,sowore,dr oracle,& others. https://t.co/bO5avCbzDn

author: Che Guevara
text:
What a silly being, you have the gut to market a man that said he will continue from where his predecessor stopped.

Is Buhari not a failure? Campaigns should base on facts and prototypes.

The only thing that gives you a little edge over mc oluomo. Is the bluetick. https://t.co/mTIPpqtPrJ

author: Che Guevara
text: Are you conceding defeat by your statement "under tinubu presidency"? https://t.co/Mk3aehv1wG

author: Che Guevara
text:
Why are you still in pain for a snub since 2014? Do you know how many Nigerians you've snubbed over the years for the party supremacy?

When you don't feel obliged to the masses over your party, why do you feel henry owes you attention because you're an Arsenal fan? https://t.co/4odwjSMrK0

author: Che Guevara
text:
Because 99% of you people are liars. You want them to continue believing you people. How easy is that for you to say?

1999 to 2023 no stable electricity, you people made governance look undoable.

Can you as a person believe someone that lied to you over the years? https://t.co/mMp5L3sr0y

author: Che Guevara
text:
My concern is so many Nigerians couldn't see what these people are, they are leeches suckling lives out of the masses. Those that were against him in 2015, will support him now. And the only people at a loss are the masses. You've been scammed over the years.

You still not ready https://t.co/Wi3PAfXCnj

author: Che Guevara
text: Only if wishes were horses. https://t.co/QtIBskJJZD

author: Che Guevara
text:
Who are those involved? Are they not police officers anymore? You said it was the police officers.

Accept you're wrong, accept that you lied. Those guys that cut her hair were not police officers. https://t.co/thQInoWpAU

author: Che Guevara
text:
This was your first comment where you alleged police officers are the ones that cut her hair.

Now, show me any police officers in the video, you can't because you lied. What's your gain from false accusations?

The whole thing got nothing to do with the police. You're a disgrace https://t.co/1vYKDZLhia

text: Good. They should be shamed in public too. https://t.co/L5qyEyhwcR
